      • pageSize

        public static Compute.MachineTypeListOption pageSize(long pageSize)
        Returns an option to specify the maximum number of machine types returned per page. pageSize must be between 0 and 500 (inclusive). If not specified 500 is used.

      • pageToken

        public static Compute.MachineTypeListOption pageToken(String pageToken)
        Returns an option to specify the page token from which to start listing machine types.

      • fields

        public static Compute.MachineTypeListOption fields(Compute.MachineTypeField... fields)
        Returns an option to specify the machine type's fields to be returned by the RPC call. If this option is not provided, all machine type's fields are returned. MachineTypeListOption.fields can be used to specify only the fields of interest. MachineType.getMachineTypeId() is always returned, even if not specified.
